                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Define Success</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Complete requirements, specifications, and test criteria generated collaboratively with your team</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">2</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Design Right</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Multiple engineering reviews catch problems when they're cheap to fix</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Build Fast</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Test-driven development with continuous validation ensures rapid, reliable progress</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">4</span>
