                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Transfer Everything</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Manufacturing files, source code, documentation - complete IP ownership transfers to you</p>
                    </div>
